{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8b424174cc","title":"中央关于印行农业生产互助合作正式决议的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0c71b626d3","index":0,"year":1953,"month":2,"day":15,"articleId":"8b424174cc","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"f7cfd13057","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央1951年12月15日关于农业生产互助合作的决议草案第十一条中这一段话的原文是：“国营农场应当推广，以发挥它的示范作用，并给互助组和合作社以技术上的援助和指导。在农民完全同意并有机器条件的地方，亦可试办少数社会主义性质的集体农庄，例如每省有一个至几个，以便取得经验，并为农民示范。1953年3月，毛泽东和中央又对这个决议作了修改，并于1953年3月26日在《人民日报》上发表。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f4b76b7ca8","type":"title","text":"中央关于印行农业生产互助合作正式决议的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7cfd13057","type":"paragraph","text":"中央各部委、中央人民政府各党组；各中央局、分局，并转各省","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3fcfd40555","type":"subtitle","text":"市委：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea254e9d48","type":"paragraph","text":"中央于一九五一年十二月所发关于农业生产互助合作的决议草案，经一年多的实施证明是正确的，应即作为正式决议，将“草案”二字删去。只将该草案第十一条内“并有机器条件”六字改为“和有适当经济条件”八字。叫此决议可即照此印行单行本。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"49d6e06a9a","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e253c0244","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十五日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":496,"end":496}}}},"__N_SSG":true}